# Little Computer 3 Virtual Machine
Written for educational and exploration purposes.
No intent on keeping fidelity with the original work.

see LICENSE

## Build and run VM (tested on Debian systems)
```
cc lc3-vm.c -O3 -o lc3-vm
./lc3-vm data/2048.obj
./lc3-vm data/rogue.obj
```

# Debug
```
cc lc3-vm.c -Wall -Wextra -Og -o lc3-vm
hexdump data/2048.obj # In another window/tab
gdb ./lc3-vm
...
(gdb) run data/2048.obj
...

```
